Stan Sabina - 341C3

Sepia filter

Pentru a citi si scrie imaginile se foloseste biblioteca stb.
Imaginile se citesc din folderul "original_images" si se scriu
in folderul "output_images" dupa aplicarea filtrului pe fiecare
pixel al imaginii.

Pentru a compila se va folosi comanda "make version"
unde version={serial, openmp, mpi, pthreads, mpi-openmp}.

Exemplu: make openmp.

Pentru a rula se va folosi comanda "make runversion"
unde version={serial, openmp, mpi, pthreads, mpi-openmp}.

Exemplu: make runopenmp.

Surse:
https://solarianprogrammer.com/2019/06/10/c-programming-reading-writing-images-stb_image-libraries/

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1926063/how-do-i-perform-arithmetic-in-a-makefile

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/45404629/makefile-count-how-many-files

